Krill project

This project has been created as an educational exploration in to Symfony 2.

The project is accompanied by several configuration files including Apache2, 
PHP 5.3 and Netbeans. The Netbeans configuration is limited to the project files
and the editor configuration, so that if one wishes to fork this project, the 
the process of configuring Netbeans to suit the coding styles in this project 
should be easier.

Most of the software and libraries used were the defaults available to Ubuntu 
11.10 at the time of writing.

This project assumes the root directory is /var/web-projects/krill/
